transcript:
Executive: Hello.
Customer: Hello, Sardar Patel Fabric Industry?
Executive: Ji.
Customer: Uh, sir Kavita Rawat baat kar rahi hu India Mart se.
Call kare the aap 9696 pe customer care pe koi problem aa rahi thi kya services se related?
Executive: Nahi nahi, shayad partner ne kiya hoga kuch shuru mein isliye kuch.
Customer: Uh.
Okay, aapke partner ke number se kiya tha. Theek hai, toh main us pe connect karu?
Executive: Toh theek hai, mam kar lijiye.
Customer: Theek hai, thank you.
